what's going on?

2
00:00:08,241 --> 00:00:10,443
‐ Those teams near Pito,
that's what.

3
00:00:10,511 --> 00:00:11,945
They're working together now.

4
00:00:12,012 --> 00:00:14,114
‐ Huh? Why would they do that?

5
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:16,316
‐ There's only one reason
I can think of.

6
00:00:16,382 --> 00:00:19,285
I bet someone called
for a cease‐fire.

7
00:00:19,352 --> 00:00:21,588
