14
00:00:38,338 --> 00:00:41,975
‐ [crowd murmuring]
‐ This is no good.

15
00:00:42,042 --> 00:00:43,777
‐ Twenty‐nine against six.

16
00:00:43,844 --> 00:00:46,847
‐ I know. But, hey, at least
this battle won't be boring.

17
00:00:46,913 --> 00:00:48,148
‐ I bet the princess

18
00:00:48,214 --> 00:00:50,483
is crapping her black cat‐suit
right about now.

19
00:00:50,551 --> 00:00:53,654
‐ True that. That chick's
a liability if I ever saw one.

20
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:55,622
‐ Women! Every time
there's a fight,

21
