Pito: <i>I'm moving in.</i>
<i>I won't be needing backup.</i>

73
00:04:40,446 --> 00:04:41,582
‐ Roger that.

74
00:04:47,688 --> 00:04:50,023
‐ <i>♪ We're all faceless</i>
<i>and anonymous... ♪</i>

75
