of those on the Japanese server.

167
00:08:50,396 --> 00:08:54,334
‐ Anti‐materiel rifles like that
are popping up more and more.

168
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:58,138
In the last B. o. B., this girl
named Sinon had a Hecate Two,

169
00:08:58,204 --> 00:08:59,740
and she kicked all the ass.

170
00:08:59,806 --> 00:09:02,576
‐ Picking those dudes off
was easy with that rifle,

171
00:09:02,643 --> 00:09:03,910
even at her distance.

172
00:09:03,977 --> 00:09:06,079
Man: I wonder what other
surprises she's got.

173
00:09:06,146 --> 00:09:07,848
‐ Now we know
one thing for sure.

174
00:09:07,914 --> 00:09:10,283
That team's gonna
destroy everyone and win.

175
00:09:10,350 --> 00:09:13,486
M's got that shield,
and those tactical‐looking mofos

176
00:09:13,554 --> 00:09:15,021
are nothing
to sneeze at, either,

177
00:09:15,088 --> 00:09:17,824
but with that woman, too,
they're unstoppable.

178
00:09:17,891 --> 00:09:20,060
The other teams are dead.
They just don't know it ye‐‐

179
00:09:20,126 --> 00:09:22,663
‐ Who cares about them?!
check out how LLENN's doing!

180
00:09:22,729 --> 00:09:23,930
Don't count her out just yet.

181
00:09:23,997 --> 00:09:25,532
As long as she's alive,

182
00:09:25,599 --> 00:09:27,901
