a chance she can win.

183
00:09:33,774 --> 00:09:36,543
LLENN: Okay, Fuka,
I'm at 100 meters.

184
00:09:36,610 --> 00:09:37,844
No enemies in sight.

185
00:09:37,911 --> 00:09:39,713
‐ [radio] <i>Roger that.</i>
<i>Light the way,</i>

186
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:41,147
<i>and I'll catch up to you.</i>

187
00:09:42,716 --> 00:09:44,017
‐ Here you go.

188
00:09:45,385 --> 00:09:46,887
‐ There's your Bullet Line.

189
00:09:46,953 --> 00:09:49,122
Heading over to you now.

190
00:09:50,557 --> 00:09:52,626
[spits] Whose idea was it

191
00:09:52,693 --> 00:09:55,128
to stick a grassy field
in this dome?

192
00:10:01,602 --> 00:10:02,636
[groans]

193
00:10:02,703 --> 00:10:04,370
I'm like a Hokkaido cockroach

194
00:10:04,437 --> 00:10:06,607
scuttling across
the kitchen floor,

195
00:10:06,673 --> 00:10:08,575
