00:10:11,477 --> 00:10:13,013
‐ We're about halfway now.

198
00:10:13,079 --> 00:10:15,816
‐ [groans]
That's as far as we got?

199
00:10:15,882 --> 00:10:18,351
‐ Sorry. We're going
as fast as we can

200
00:10:18,418 --> 00:10:19,720
using the Bullet Line trick.

201
00:10:19,786 --> 00:10:21,922
Besides, it's safer in here.

202
00:10:21,988 --> 00:10:24,525
If we'd gone
around the north side,

203
00:10:24,591 --> 00:10:26,560
we would have bumped into MMTM,

204
00:10:26,627 --> 00:10:28,428
and South,
it would have been SHINC.

205
00:10:28,494 --> 00:10:32,132
Going through the dome is
the fastest way to get to Pito

206
00:10:32,198 --> 00:10:33,299
and the safest.

207
00:10:33,366 --> 00:10:36,770
‐ So what about the three teams
in here with us?

208
00:10:36,837 --> 00:10:39,673
‐ Yeah, them. I guess
this is where we find out

209
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:41,742
how lucky I am or not.

210
00:10:41,808 --> 00:10:43,644
Are you sure your wings

211
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,478
