and shoot while you fly.

213
00:10:48,849 --> 00:10:50,817
‐ Nope, sorry.

214
00:10:50,884 --> 00:10:54,320
I gave up all my fairy skills
to come help you out here.

215
00:10:54,387 --> 00:10:55,889
[automatic gunfire]

216
00:10:57,658 --> 00:10:59,392
‐ Hmm.

217
00:10:59,459 --> 00:11:01,394
