totally work out for us.

222
00:11:09,803 --> 00:11:12,839
Keep up the good work, guys.
Wipe each other out.

223
00:11:14,207 --> 00:11:17,210
‐ No. It's weird, real weird.

224
00:11:17,277 --> 00:11:20,046
Something's not right
about the way they're shooting.

225
00:11:20,113 --> 00:11:21,347
‐ Like what?

226
00:11:21,414 --> 00:11:24,017
‐ Like this is a trap.

227
00:11:24,084 --> 00:11:25,719
You see those three teams?

228
00:11:25,786 --> 00:11:27,888
I bet you anything
they're working together,

229
00:11:27,954 --> 00:11:30,190
just like the ones
going after Pito.

230
00:11:30,256 --> 00:11:32,626
