on the last scan

231
00:11:32,693 --> 00:11:34,294
and figured we'd
cut through the dome.

232
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:37,964
‐ Ooh, you're so popular!
This is getting exciting.

233
00:11:38,031 --> 00:11:40,934
So how do you know
it's a trap?

234
00:11:41,001 --> 00:11:43,670
‐ You saw where the three
team leaders were on the map,

235
00:11:43,737 --> 00:11:45,471
so it's kinda weird
all that gunfire

236
00:11:45,539 --> 00:11:47,574
is coming from the same
direction and distance.

237
00:11:47,641 --> 00:11:51,645
The only explanation
is they're all shooting
from the same position.

238
00:11:51,712 --> 00:11:54,414
‐ Wow, you sure have sharp ears.

239
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,149
So what do you wanna do?

240
00:11:56,216 --> 00:11:58,885
Sneak up from behind and
blast 'em back to the saloon?

241
00:11:58,952 --> 00:12:01,855
‐ No. I don't want to waste
my ammo on these guys.

242
00:12:01,922 --> 00:12:03,924
If we keep moving
and be careful,

243
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:05,191
we can avoid them.

244
